<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="1" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#add8ff" WIDTH="150"><B>Analysis</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">The sole question before the court is<BR ALIGN='left'/>whether the transfer of the Aero Chem<BR ALIGN='left'/>stock by plaintiffs was a nontaxable<BR ALIGN='left'/>reorganization pursuant to § 368(a) (1)<BR ALIGN='left'/>(B).</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
