<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLBORDER="1" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="4">
  <TR><TD BGCOLOR="#add8ff" WIDTH="150"><B>Analysis</B></TD></TR>
  <TR><TD ALIGN="left" WIDTH="150">Here, the exchange of the twenty per<BR ALIGN='left'/>cent (20%) interest in Aero Chem was<BR ALIGN='left'/>conducted in two steps: first, a twenty<BR ALIGN='left'/>per cent (20%) interest in Aero Chem was<BR ALIGN='left'/>exchanged for Chem-Atom stock; and,<BR ALIGN='left'/>second, the Chem-Atom stock was<BR ALIGN='left'/>exchanged for Pfaudler stock.</TD></TR>
